{
  "texts": [
    "Thorough Comparisons with RAG.",
    "Overall, the LLM can generate better responses with retrieved entities by all tested retrievers.",
    "However, even if advanced retrievers use more data for training and increase the embedding dimension to obtain better embeddings, their focus remains exclusively on the text domain, creating a performance bottleneck as no topological information is retrieved.",
    "As shown in Table 2, when graph context is not considered, there is only a slight difference in the enhancement achieved by various retrievers.",
    "This phenomenon is further discussed in Appendix A.4."
  ]
}